Tom Irwin (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tom_Irwin_(actor) 0 Tom Irwin (born June 1, 1956) is an American film, television, and stage actor. Irwin is best known for his roles as Adrian Powell in the Lifetime comedy-drama series Devious Maids and as Graham Chase in the mid-1990s drama My So-Called Life.
